1) Create system user happy flow.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- The user is redirected to the "Create System User" page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin0000» in the «Username» field.
- Enter "Ssmog790" in the "Password" and "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- Redirected to «System User List» page.
- Make sure the account has been created.
Post-condition:
- Delete a previously created new user.

2) Creating a system user with empty fields.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Clear the "Username", "Password", "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Browser errors about unfilled fields exist.
- The browser error message contains correct text.

3) Creating a new user with a password of only numbers.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin0000» in the «Username» field.
- Enter «1234567890» in the "Password" and "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message «This password is too common.» appeared.
- Error message «This password is entirely numeric.» appeared.

4) Creating a new user where username and password have the same text.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin0000» in the «Username», «Password», «Repeat password» fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message «The password is too similar to the username.» appeared.

5) Creating a new user with a short password.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin0000» in the «Username» field.
- Enter «smog» in the "Password" and "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message «This password is too short. It must contain at least 8 characters.» appeared.

6) Creating a new user with different text in the password fields.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin0000» in the «Username» field.
- Enter «Ssmog790» in the «Password» field.
- Enter «Ssmog890» in the «Repeat password» field.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message «The two password fields didn’t match.» appeared.

7) Creating a new user with a username that already exists.
Pre-condition:
- Creating a new user with «admin0000» username.
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin0000» in the «Username» field.
- Enter "Ssmog790" in the "Password" and "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message « A user with that username already exists. » appeared.

8) Creating a new user with illegal characters in username.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin^» in the «Username» field.
- Enter «Ssmog790» in the "Password" and "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message «Enter a valid username. This value may contain only letters, numbers, and @/./+/-/_ characters.» appeared.

9) Creating a new user with a username exceeding 150 characters.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter a random text of 151 characters in the "Username" field.
- Enter «Ssmog790» in the "Password" and "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message « Ensure this value has at most 150 characters (it has 151).» appeared.

10) Creating a user with a common password.
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Navigate to dashboard page.
- Click «System Users» button from Menu bar.
- In the additional menu, press the "New System User" button.
- Redirected to «Create System User» page.
Step definition:
- Enter «admin0000» in the «Username» field.
-  Enter «password» in the "Password" and "Repeat password" fields.
- Click «Confirm» button.
Expected result:
- The user remains on the "Create System User" page.
- Error message « This password is too common.» appeared.